= redhat用iso做yum源 =

 1. 挂载ISO文件
  {{{
#mount -o loop RHEL_5.7\ x86_64.iso /media}}}
 1. 增加一个REPO文件
  {{{
# vi /etc/yum.repos.d/abc.repo
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Server]
name=rhel6server
baseurl=file:///media/Server
enable=1
gpcheck=1
gpgkey=file:///media/Server/RPM-GPG-KEY-redhat-release
}}}
 1. 更新源
  {{{
#yum update
}}}

----
